summary:
Background in Cardiology and Cardiac Surgery where he successfully coordinated and
managed global clinical trials at medical device companies. 

Successful Medical Affairs Manager with over 20 years’ experience: 11 years in a university hospital
environment and a further 15 in the Medical Device industry. 

Master of Science in Health Sciences.
PhD degree in Medicine

Involved in a number of new product developments (medical devices)
